---
const article = {
  url: "https://preagi.substack.com/p/take-on-ai",
  title: "Common Sense × AI: A Non-SWE's take on the pre-agi era",
  subtitle: "The real moat isn't code — it's judgment.",
  cover: "/take-on-ai-cover.jpg",
};
---

<section class="mb-8 sm:mb-10">
  <h2 class="mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] accent mb-1">
    Latest writing
  </h2>
  <p class="mono text-xs muted mb-6">May 2026</p>
  <div class="prose text-lg leading-[1.7]">
    <p>
      <span class="accent">Everyone is a builder now</span>. The bottleneck
      used to be coding skill, design skill, and distribution. The tools just
      collapsed those. What's left is wanting to do something specific and
      doing it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <a
    href={article.url}
    target="_blank"
    rel="noreferrer"
    class="block mt-8"
    style="border-bottom: none"
  >
    <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-elev)] p-5 sm:p-6">
      <p class="mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] muted mb-4">
        From Substack · @preagi
      </p>
      <img
        src={article.cover}
        alt={article.title}
        width="1248"
        height="832"
        loading="lazy"
        class="w-full h-auto block"
      />
      <p class="text-xl font-medium leading-snug mt-4">
        {article.title}
      </p>
      <p class="muted text-base leading-relaxed mt-2">
        {article.subtitle}
      </p>
      <p class="mono text-xs accent mt-3 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
        Read on Substack →
      </p>
    </div>
  </a>
</section>
